    "body": "This PR fixes the out-of-bound K/V value loading in the FA3 `sparse_mainloop.cuh`, which may cause a nan value for `BatchPrefillWithPagedKVCacheSM90Run` and `BlockSparseAttentionWrapper `. The accumulation of out-of-bound V and S causes the nan value.\r\n\r\nThis may solve the issue https://github.com/flashinfer-ai/flashinfer/issues/1018.",
